{"tid":1504972,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴重警告左膠人士","createTime":"2019-08-25T12:23:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T13:09:47.000Z","uid":266685,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a38dfa0eb64ca02bfd898a1b8274e1a0181150ed","tid":1504972,"uid":266685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:23:01.000Z","msg":"咪撚再阻住勇武手足教訓班黑社會<br />\n係唔係唔記得721？<br />\n係唔係唔記得85被斬到隻腳永失知覺個手足？<br />\n係唔係唔記得福建幫群毆年輕人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地面對緊既係黑社會啊 <br />\n仲要係有黑警，政府，司法部門同成個司法制度包庇既黑社會啊！<br />\n班人毫無道德底線咁斬傷我地既手足 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而你班仆街左膠居然叫人唔好打！？ </span></strong></span><br />\n點撚樣啊 企係到用愛與正義去捱斬啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警告你班左膠咪再阻住教訓黑社會 班黑社會打死都唔抵可憐 <br />\n你地再阻住手足教訓黑社會 只會令佢地更猖狂 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">遲早被斬既就係你</span></strong></span><br />\n你要做大愛人士 就用你既身軀去擋刀 企定比人斬 咪再阻住晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆、不分化、但勿做豬隊友</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"593df654d373007209588b0a95fa0bd29665061d","tid":1504972,"uid":266685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:24:21.000Z","msg":"P牌自推10連"},{"pid":"ada4b4a441a13cf005bb3082c8da2330cbcaf37b","tid":1504972,"uid":266685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:24:31.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"fa8c87657c5ca1a1c6f44f1a1236131d7490c1bf","tid":1504972,"uid":266685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:24:44.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"f8ef76f830a22f7eb06d67399b95ccd062973ea7","tid":1504972,"uid":266685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:24:55.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"e99e98ffc3a7e454a00a3b73d933c3dfba918ebb","tid":1504972,"uid":1315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:25:00.000Z","msg":"左膠係核彈黎 雨傘輸左膠 魚蛋輸左膠<br />\n立法會果時又係有左膠 好彩比人拉走左<br />\n<br />\n記得 左膠唔係我地敵人 但係麻煩在場手足拉撚走哂佢地 唔好阻住前線做野"},{"pid":"d2d157f39fa95d2523b8cc789075db3365f58268","tid":1504972,"uid":266685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:25:07.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"9ae227d710f6c49ad8d1bdba97b3fc62bf8ce9ea","tid":1504972,"uid":266685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:25:17.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"1cd7981f77d3fb134258102470ef719c9306b9d0","tid":1504972,"uid":266685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e99e98ffc3a7e454a00a3b73d933c3dfba918ebb","tid":1504972,"uid":1315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:25:00.000Z","msg":"左膠係核彈黎 雨傘輸左膠 魚蛋輸左膠<br />\n立法會果時又係有左膠 好彩比人拉走左<br />\n<br />\n記得 左膠唔係我地敵人 但係麻煩在場手足拉撚走哂佢地 唔好阻住前線做野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:25:36.000Z","msg":"岩 唔係敵人 但唔好做豬隊友拖累手足"},{"pid":"a1823b9f312def501627da0f6d1246e53d632338","tid":1504972,"uid":266685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:25:47.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"95f3eca2c44ab97b7bcec124ac67d8bf9e58bf69","tid":1504972,"uid":266685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:26:03.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"dd536a919f27ce49b58b03897ba0dac0fbf9bb71","tid":1504972,"uid":266685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:26:15.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"e3c936601b3d6f592b8d641817ad4b6b7cb1a90f","tid":1504972,"uid":266685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:26:25.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"bdd5f3eb39f0b23cb89ea784a981f73cd4c79f67","tid":1504972,"uid":266685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:26:36.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"ba946feab879b8b8ab83caaef78b9de2353acc3a","tid":15